titles.title: A concurrent resolution supporting National Men's Health Week.
A concurrent resolution supporting National Men's Health Week.

action.text: Referred to the Committee on Health, Education, Labor, and Pensions.

committee.name: Senate Health, Education, Labor, and Pensions

bill.summary: Resolves that the Congress supports National Men's Health Week. Requests that the President call on the American public and interested groups to observe National Men's Health Week with appropriate ceremonies and activities.
